profile:
Double T Contracting specializes in complete home remodeling and renovations. Our design and build team has helped many home owners upgrade and update their homes style to a Modern, Traditional, Contemporary or Classic look and feel. We believe each home is unique, which is why we tailor your custom home renovation project to suit your lifestyle and family needs. We can update your kitchen, bathroom or your entire house and manage the project and cost to be within your time frame and budget. 

At Double T Contracting we offer the highest craftsmanship and use quality materials in order to deliver you an exciting design with superior fit and finish, while increasing your home’s value.


Our design and build team knowledge can turn the most sophisticated and complex renovation project into reality and make the whole process enjoyable and stress free for you. Our Design and Build process allows us to work one on one with you, keeping you informed about each major step of the project from initiation to completion. 

Let us pay attention to all the details and make your dream a reality.

We offer a wide variety of services including the construction and installation of custom docks and decks, custom interiors, exterior additions and new construction. At Riverside Renos, you will work alongside our team who will help bring your vision to life, providing an upfront and detailed quote as well as an organized timeline for your project(s).  With a reputation that speaks for itself, our hardworking team is ready to fulfill your design dreams.     
                                                                                                                              
                  
Below are some of the services we offer:
          
• Custom Decks
• Custom Docks: Floating Systems, Pole Systems, Tower Dock Systems, Custom Aluminum Construction, etc.
• Custom Interiors: Basement, Kitchen, Bathroom, Flooring, etc.
• Exterior Additions
• New Construction

Looking for Recommended Handyman Services in the Simcoe Muskoka Region? Look No Further!
Not everyone has the expertise to tackle those tricky home renovations or overdue cottage repairs by themselves. With Agnew Contracting on board, completing that work in the shortest amount of time has never been simpler.

About Us
My name is Tyler, and I’m the owner-operator of Agnew Contracting, along with my wife, Janelle. James C. Hildebrandt

profile:
Property Services/Handyman Services and more.......    

Beacon Service Solutions main business goal is customer satisfaction bar none. Progressive,innovative and responsive we accept any job large or small with one focus... to exceed your expectations.

 Our company prides itself on keeping to a schedule, and going about our work in your home or business in a respectful, and unobtrusive manner.

We are truly a "Jack of all Trades" business with a personal touch. We can repair existing conditions with a minimal budget or install new at your request. Over 25 years experience in residential and commercial, all season, indoor and outdoor property maintenance/management.

Our services include but are not limited to:

~ Off season vacation home security and insurance requirement check ups including rural, remote, island, and difficult access locations. Ask about our cottage open and closing services including monthly off seasons check ups which includes a short report with  photo sent to you via e-mail. 

 ~Property maintenance, electrical, plumbing, mechanical repair/install/rework.

 ~Custom cabinetry, and custom furniture. Co-Designing/building/installation.

~ Interior and exterior professional cleaning services.

Some of our specialization's include:

 ~Log Home renovations.
 
 -Bathroom Renovations.

 ~Hideaway beds/ Murphy Beds.

... Let us make your dreams reality!
